# paste(itemProviders:)

**Instance Method**

Performs a paste operation on the responder object.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor optional func paste(itemProviders: [NSItemProvider])
```

## Parameters

- **itemProviders**: An array of [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSItemProvider] objects.

## Discussion

This method performs a paste operation on the responder object, pasting the data provided by specified item providers.

## Performing a paste operation

- **canPaste(_:)**: Returns a Boolean value that determines whether the responder object can perform a paste operation using data provided by the item providers.
